channel.title: 517 Client need help! How to change ip?
channel.description: How do you change the ip on a 517 client? I want to change it to my ip for my 517 server but idk how?? it doesn't have 127.0.0.1 or 0.0.0.0 or nothing, I've tried searching .biz .org. .com in the client.java and Applet_Sub1 but couldn't find nothing, is there a different way your oppose to do it? Please help! Thanks :)
